.Dd $Mdocdate: April 1 2018 $
.Dt BCMDOG 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm bcmdog
.Nd Broadcom BCM283x watchdog timer
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "bcmdog* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the integrated watchdog timer in the Broadcom
BCM2835, BCM2836 and BCM2837 SoCs.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr watchdog 4 ,
.Xr watchdogd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.1 .
